<span id="Description"></span>
== 概要 ==

The [[Image:Sketcher_ViewSection.svg|16px]] [[Sketcher_ViewSection|Sketcher ViewSection]] tool toggles a temporary section plane that hides any objects and parts of objects in front of the sketch plane while the sketch is in edit mode. This is a per-sketch setting stored in the {{PropertyView|Section View}} property of sketches.

[[File:Sketcher ViewSection1.png|300px]] [[File:Sketcher ViewSection2.png|300px]]
{{Caption|Partially hidden sketch and fully visible sketch}}

<span id="Usage"></span>
== 使い方 ==

See also: [[Sketcher_Preferences#Display|Sketcher Preferences]].

# This tool is only available if a sketch is in [[Sketcher_EditSketch|edit mode]].
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:Sketcher_ViewSection.svg|16px]] [[Sketcher_ViewSection|View section]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Sketch → [[Image:Sketcher_ViewSection.svg|16px]] View section}} option from the menu.


